		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>Well, i cant really dipute anything you have said since they are your personal opinions and are entirely valid.  However, i happen to like alot of the things you dislike.<br />
<br />
Stupid people:  I think this is more of a result that the game is new and alot of MMO newbs are playing the game.  As the game and players mature the "stupid" people should be less evident.  Ohh, they'll still be stupid people.....they will just play the game better.<br />
<br />
AH: yes, it certainly is lacking.  Hopefully the continue to add functionality to it in future patches.<br />
<br />
Equipment:  I perfer WoW's itemization to EQ's in general.  There arent huge gaps in player ability due solely to equipment.  I like the fact that a casual player outfitted in full strat/scholo/UBRS gear will be able to perform just as well as a player outfitted in full MC/Onxyia gear.  Now it does take a bit away from the powergamer achiever types......but it also doenst put up a huge roadblock for newer players joinging in on the raiding ranks.<br />
<br />
Elves:  You're completely wrong here.....the fact that there are elves to begin with  sucks ass.   Goddamn fairy elves.  (but seriously, try to think of the lore as less Tolkien and a little more origional, will make living in the world easier)<br />
<br />
Lag: It certainly can be bad at times.....but it has been improving steadily over the last month or two.  I expect it to continue to get better.</div>
	</td>
</tr>
