Herbs, yes.  Mines, no.<br />
Herbs are one-shot, one-harvest.<br />
Mines can result in 1-4 seperate loot windows, and can be mined by more than one person.<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
