</div>
Yes.<br />
Engineering creates a plan which smiths need to make, so engineers can use the result.<br />
Tailoring and engineering use a lot of skins.<br />
Leatherworking uses a bunch of different cloth types.<br />
Tailoring, engineering, and leatherworking all use different potions.<br />
