Maybe as a mage spirit isn't important for you but i can assure as a priest in the end game, having 150 spirit is crippling compared to the priest with 300. This is most likely due to spirit being perhaps the number 2, possibly number 1, stat for our class. It will take you twice as long, and that could be a matter of seconds or minutes, to regen your mana with 150 spirit over 300. In a place like MC, this could mean life or death for the raid as several healers in unison keeping up their mana is required. If one healer fails to make the cut, the others will have to pick up the slack but that can only be done so much before they too need to regen.
			
